body:
Evaluates to a boolean that is `true` if the Function is running as
a system user.

```javascript
exports = function() {
   const isSystemUser = context.runningAsSystem()
   if(isSystemUser) {
      // Do some work with the system user.
   } else {
      // Fail.
   }
}
```

